summary: The last episode titles are out and I'm scared
body:
The last episode titles are out and I’m scared

So “A Moving day” and “We were here”…

I saw the theory around here that maybe Andi could be moving… Well, whatever happens in the last episodes, I just want to be sure that my children are happy and all together in the AM universe after the show ends.

I mean I trust Terri. But I also don’t. I’m sure she will mess with our feelings.

Anyway, less than two weeks and were back guys. Also, I send some love to everyone who’s reading this ♡
